{"tid":2249354,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Phone 12 官方維修價格公佈 有／無保養下爆芒、換電池價錢","createTime":"2020-10-19T09:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T10:30:51.000Z","uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a1e43bb5cfbcc12c53015c3586e51e3ca46e3ee","tid":2249354,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:37:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d4884978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fd4884978.jpg&h=fd4af289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niPhone 12 在 16 日正式接受預訂，而 Apple 亦在其後於官網公布 iPhone 12 和 iPhone 12 Pro 熒幕維修與電池維修的價格，基本上與 iPhone 11 Pro 相同。<br />\n<br />\niPhone 12 系列共四款機型採用「超 Retina XDR 顯示器」，使得 iPhone 12 在螢幕維修價格有所提升，據官網所指，兩款 6.1 吋機型 iPhone 12 和 iPhone 12 Pro 在已過保養期後（或任何其他非保養範圍內的損壞）的熒幕維修價格皆為 HKD$2,139，與 iPhone 11 Pro、iPhone XS和iPhone X 的熒幕維修價格相同，但比 iPhone 11 和 iPhone XR 貴，該兩款機型只需 $1539 即可更換熒幕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-10-19-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.49.13-694x299.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-10-19-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.49.13-694x299.png&h=99942034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，官網目前尚未公布 5.4 吋 iPhone 12 mini 與 6.7 吋 iPhone 12 Pro Max 的熒幕更換維修費用，不過預計 iPhone 12 Pro Max 的收費應該會與 iPhone 11 Pro Max 和 iPhone XS Max 一樣，更換費用可能是 HKD$2579。<br />\n<br />\n至於電池方面，只要在保養期內，或在 AppleCare+ 服務計劃範圍內，即可在需要（總電池容量低於 80%）時免費更換電池，不過在已過保養期的情況下， 則需收取 HKD$549 的更換費用 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-10-19-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.46.54-694x568.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-10-19-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.46.54-694x568.png&h=a535bd76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用戶只要購買價值 HKD$1399 的 AppleCare+ 服務，即可總共獲得 24 個月的 AppleCare+ 保養，而期間每 12 個月最多有兩次意外損壞保養服務。雖然某些人為損壞如熒幕維修等仍而付費，但就只要收取 HKD$228 ，其他損壞則收取 HKD$788 服務費。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Apple </strong>"},{"pid":"24e0de4393b04a29844c7c81113f499006d90d6c","tid":2249354,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d6d910c40c38a33ab171038761e08cd1f95411","tid":2249354,"uid":23162,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"屌你呢乜濕鳩嘢都要報新聞？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85684dd6714fa864302dc732a8458c042759321d","tid":2249354,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82d6d910c40c38a33ab171038761e08cd1f95411","tid":2249354,"uid":23162,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"屌你呢乜濕鳩嘢都要報新聞？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"咩19嘢，你部iphone唔會壞唔會跌咁撚把砲？"},{"pid":"a181639d861db3d5a1c202a5e6a60af1ae87f1ed","tid":2249354,"uid":175208,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82d6d910c40c38a33ab171038761e08cd1f95411","tid":2249354,"uid":23162,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"屌你呢乜濕鳩嘢都要報新聞？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"咁都唔撚報得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}